headline: Tyler Technologies’ State Partner Receives 2025 StateScoop 50 Award from Scoop News Group
summary: PLANO, Texas, May 01, 2025--Tyler announces its state partner in Nebraska has won the 2025 State IT Innovation of the Year award in Scoop News Group’s StateScoop 50 Awards.
